# Releases ARE committed (so the prebuilt zip ships with the source).
# CI also produces the same artifact on every run.
!releases/

# But the per-machine "unpacked install" folder is not tracked — it's the
# stable load path users (and the maintainer) point Chrome at, kept free of
# version numbers so the extension ID never changes.
releases/tabtastic/

